title: Pro Pinball - Big Race USA
description:
Features:

1-click installer
Patched to last version (1.18)
No-CD crack applied
Manual.pdf included
FoxitReader.exe included (no install)
Rulesheet.txt included
Straight-to-table shortcut
Options tweaked


Notes:

To reset all options to defaults simply delete "wgame.cfg".
To restore my settings make a new copy of "wgame.cfg" from "wgame.cfg.bak".
If the sound or keyboard input is not working properly,
enable Win98 compatibility mode in the shortcut properties.


Requirements:

Windows 95 / NT4.0
Pentium 90MHz
16MB RAM
563MB HDD
